Template: curvedns/ask_fqdn
Type: string
_Description: Fully Qualified Domain Name (FQDN):
 Please specify the Fully Qualified Domain Name (FQDN) that curvedns will
 be available on. A corresponding private key will be generated in
 "/etc/curvedns/env/CURVEDNS_PRIVATE_KEY" - see curvedns-keygen(1).
 .
 You should also save your authoritative name server name, DNS public key
 and secret key somewhere safe.
 .
 Next, edit "/etc/default/curvedns" to fit your needs before restarting the
 server.

